Definition: a clear and telling mental image
Example: he described his mental picture of his assailant; he had no clear picture of himself or his world; the events left a permanent impression in his mind
Synonyms: picture, verb, creation, impression, image, a, clear, and, telling, mental, he, described, his, of, assailant, had, no, himself, or, world, the, events, left, permanent, in, mind
Category: noun.cognition
